♪Watch as everything drowns in shadows♪

6
00:00:17,460 --> 00:00:19,340
♪Have no fear, do not retreat♪

7
00:00:19,940 --> 00:00:23,220
♪See the blazing sparks ignite♪

8
00:00:24,620 --> 00:00:27,060
♪Believe this all has cause and effect♪

9
00:00:27,100 --> 00:00:29,460
♪No evil escapes untouched♪

10
00:00:29,500 --> 00:00:31,820
♪From the stormy torrents in this life♪

11
