124.

17
00:01:57,020 --> 00:01:58,400
[Zhu Mao's Personal Information]

18
00:01:58,400 --> 00:01:59,920
(Zhu Mao's background is unclear.)

19
00:02:00,800 --> 00:02:03,880
(He was originally a gang member
active in the underworld of Guangzhou.)

20
00:02:05,280 --> 00:02:07,000
(Cunning)

21
00:02:07,560 --> 00:02:08,640
(and vicious,)

22
00:02:08,880 --> 00:02:09,840
(he is ruthless and merciless.)

23
00:02:11,080 --> 00:02:12,400
(After years of operation,)

24
00:02:12,800 --> 00:02:14,200
(he transformed himself
into a wealthy merchant)

25
00:02:14,600 --> 00:02:16,960
(secretly trafficking humans.)

26
00:02:16,960 --> 00:02:18,520
[Information of Human Trafficking]

27
00:02:18,520 --> 00:02:20,000
(Zhu Mao even schemed)

28
00:02:20,120 --> 00:02:23,200
(to secretly murder Zhou Jishu,
a rich businessman in Guangzhou,)

29
00:02:23,640 --> 00:02:25,960
(and took his wife, Chen Peiqin.)

30
00:02:26,480 --> 00:02:30,040
(At that time, Zhou Jishu's son
Zhou Guanwen was still very young,)

31
00:02:30,560 --> 00:02:33,360
(but Zhu Mao forced him
to accept this murderer as his father.)

32
00:02:35,080 --> 00:02:36,920
(Using the ill-gotten wealth,)

33
00:02:37,360 --> 00:02:39,280
(Zhu Mao expanded
the human trafficking business,)

34
00:02:39,680 --> 00:02:42,000
(impacting the entire Lianhe Town.)

35
00:02:50,760 --> 00:02:54,520
As expected,
the only one who can find it is you,

36
00:02:54,520 --> 00:02:55,960
Xue Tong.

37
00:02:57,840 --> 00:02:59,680
You've been guarding this old house
for so many years.

38
00:03:00,520 --> 00:03:01,960
It's for the sake of
this incriminating evidence, isn't it?

39
00:03:02,800 --> 00:03:03,600
Xue Tong,

40
00:03:05,480 --> 00:03:08,360
you should have died in that fire.

41
00:03:08,800 --> 00:03:13,000
I allowed you to get rid of Qian Tong,
Yang Jian, and Dou Huaizhong

42
00:03:13,640 --> 00:03:15,800
because it's just my counterplot.

43
00:03:16,200 --> 00:03:17,800
You bewitched my son

44
00:03:18,640 --> 00:03:20,400
and sowed discord between us.

45
00:03:20,800 --> 00:03:22,840
I certainly won't spare you.

46
00:03:25,000 --> 00:03:26,120
Then tell me,

47
00:03:27,080 --> 00:03:28,200
how do you explain this?

48
00:03:29,560 --> 00:03:30,520
Since you know,

49
00:03:30,880 --> 00:03:31,880
I won't hide the truth from you.

50
00:03:32,560 --> 00:03:36,080
Actually, your father and I
were best friends in childhood.

51
00:03:36,760 --> 00:03:38,880
Unfortunately, he passed away
at a young age.

52
00:03:39,480 --> 00:03:43,160
Seeing you and your mother so pitiful,
I took you in.

53
00:03:43,800 --> 00:03:47,880
All this time,
I have taken great care of you two

54
00:03:48,240 --> 00:03:49,600
with a clear conscience.

55
00:03:55,200 --> 00:03:56,160
Died at a young age?

56
00:03:56,600 --> 00:03:58,160
The dead cannot give witness, right?

57
00:03:59,800 --> 00:04:00,560
Then let me ask you,

58
00:04:02,640 --> 00:04:03,520
did you

59
00:04:05,520 --> 00:04:07,440
kill my mom or not?

60
00:04:08,400 --> 00:04:09,400
She can swim,

61
00:04:09,760 --> 00:04:11,560
but she died in the pond of Zhu Manor.

62
00:04:11,560 --> 00:04:13,040
Yet you tell me this was an accident?

63
00:04:13,040 --> 00:04:13,840
Zhu Guanwen!

64
00:04:16,440 --> 00:04:21,120
After so many years of raising you,
spoiling you, and protecting you,

65
00:04:21,120 --> 00:04:22,800
you actually dare
to talk to me like this?

66
00:04:23,480 --> 00:04:25,040
You ungrateful brat,

67
00:04:25,040 --> 00:04:27,000
you will face the consequences!

68
00:04:30,800 --> 00:04:32,600
You're still trying to lie
at this point.

69
00:04:34,840 --> 00:04:35,480
Long,

70
00:04:36,760 --> 00:04:38,240
tie them both up!

71
00:04:38,440 --> 00:04:38,920
Yes!

72
00:04:54,840 --> 00:04:55,720
What are you looking at?

73
00:04:56,080 --> 00:04:57,040
Kill me if you can.

74
00:04:57,320 --> 00:05:00,280
You are my son. How can I kill you?

75
00:05:00,680 --> 00:05:02,960
But I will discipline you well

76
00:05:02,960 --> 00:05:04,120
to let you understand

77
00:05:04,760 --> 00:05:06,720
who your family is.

78
00:05:06,920 --> 00:05:07,600
Family?

79
00:05:09,640 --> 00:05:12,200
You have blood on your hands.

80
00:05:12,680 --> 00:05:14,760
How many lives
you've killed over the years?

81
00:05:15,440 --> 00:05:16,800
Do you have a conscience?

82
00:05:19,040 --> 00:05:20,960
Those lives are worthless.

83
00:05:21,600 --> 00:05:23,040
Why did I need to keep them?

84
00:05:23,280 --> 00:05:25,240
I sold them to Southeast Asia

85
00:05:25,840 --> 00:05:28,360
to give them
a chance to start a new life.

86
00:05:28,880 --> 00:05:30,320
To start a new life?

87
00:05:31,600 --> 00:05:33,280
You are still full of chicanery.

88
00:05:33,680 --> 00:05:35,040
You are doing this just for money.

89
00:05:35,040 --> 00:05:36,600
You'll do anything for money!

90
00:05:37,040 --> 00:05:37,840
Zhu Mao,

91
00:05:39,360 --> 00:05:41,960
you wouldn't even
spare the women and children.

92
00:05:42,680 --> 00:05:44,080
Do you deserve to be a human being?

93
00:05:44,080 --> 00:05:45,240
So what?

94
00:05:46,760 --> 00:05:48,560
They can make money for me,

95
00:05:48,760 --> 00:05:50,320
big money!

96
00:05:50,680 --> 00:05:54,280
With money, I can rule Lianhe Town

97
00:05:54,480 --> 00:05:55,920
and do whatever I want!

98
00:05:57,920 --> 00:05:58,920
What about my father?

99
00:05:59,080 --> 00:06:00,720
What did he do?

100
00:06:02,440 --> 00:06:05,080
Because he knew too much truth.

101
00:06:05,080 --> 00:06:06,920
Just because of that,
you killed the whole Xue family!

102
00:06:07,520 --> 00:06:08,400
Guanwen,

103
00:06:09,320 --> 00:06:11,240
you are still too naive.

104
00:06:11,600 --> 00:06:12,520
You should know

105
00:06:12,720 --> 00:06:14,080
that in this world,

106
00:06:15,080 --> 00:06:16,800
only winners

107
00:06:17,120 --> 00:06:18,680
can live to the end.

108
00:06:19,720 --> 00:06:21,120
If you want to climb high,

109
00:06:21,560 --> 00:06:26,320
you must know that showing mercy
will lead to future troubles.

110
00:06:26,320 --> 00:06:27,280
Therefore,

111
00:06:27,520 --> 00:06:28,400
when you do anything,

112
00:06:29,080 --> 00:06:30,800
you must be ruthless.

113
00:06:31,320 --> 00:06:32,320
Then tell me,

114
00:06:33,880 --> 00:06:34,760
why did you keep me alive?

115
00:06:34,760 --> 00:06:36,440
I don't care if you agree or not,

116
00:06:38,160 --> 00:06:40,280
but Peiqin was the woman
I loved the most,

117
00:06:41,640 --> 00:06:44,480
and you must be my son.

118
00:06:46,600 --> 00:06:47,600
I see now.

119
00:06:48,040 --> 00:06:50,440
You hate those homeless kids

120
00:06:50,600 --> 00:06:51,280
because

121
00:06:51,280 --> 00:06:53,040
you're one of them.

122
00:06:53,320 --> 00:06:54,160
Shut your mouth!

123
00:06:55,840 --> 00:06:57,680
You are just like your father,

124
00:06:58,640 --> 00:06:59,760
not cherishing opportunities.

125
00:07:01,080 --> 00:07:02,720
I gave him a chance,

126
00:07:03,480 --> 00:07:05,520
and I gave you one, too.

127
00:07:06,720 --> 00:07:07,520
Son,

128
00:07:08,680 --> 00:07:11,240
only by this woman dying before you

129
00:07:11,520 --> 00:07:12,680
can you understand

130
00:07:12,680 --> 00:07:14,000
my good intentions and love for you.

131
00:07:14,000 --> 00:07:14,600
No!

132
00:07:22,620 --> 00:07:25,140
♪The end has now been reached♪

133
00:07:25,420 --> 00:07:28,060
♪Yet we face each other in silence♪

134
00:07:28,760 --> 00:07:31,380
♪Looking away from you♪

135
00:07:31,420 --> 00:07:35,460
♪Emotions like a flood
they spread and grew♪

136
00:07:35,620 --> 00:07:38,940
♪Who would like to be fooled♪

137
00:07:40,020 --> 00:07:44,000
♪Love, how could it be a lie♪

138
00:07:47,620 --> 00:07:50,580
♪In a moment♪

139
00:07:50,620 --> 00:07:53,480
♪Flitting images flashing♪

140
00:07:53,780 --> 00:07:55,860
♪Eyes fall shut♪

141
00:07:56,060 --> 00:07:59,700
♪Fingertips gently touched♪

142
00:08:00,520 --> 00:08:03,080
♪Risking fate and danger venturing♪

143
00:08:03,120 --> 00:08:05,000
♪Dancing on the tip of the knife♪

144
00:08:05,120 --> 00:08:11,280
♪Put on a show wholeheartedly♪

145
00:08:12,180 --> 00:08:15,420
♪In a moment♪

146
00:08:15,460 --> 00:08:18,340
♪The memory in my mind♪

147
00:08:18,500 --> 00:08:20,260
♪Surging at me♪

148
00:08:20,340 --> 00:08:24,620
♪Beliefs hidden deep inside♪

149
00:08:24,860 --> 00:08:27,740
♪In an abyss perhaps inescapable♪

150
00:08:27,980 --> 00:08:30,900
♪Under a ray of light in the darkness♪

151
00:08:30,940 --> 00:08:33,860
♪I may reopen my eyes♪
